{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#6038: KeepAlive provide function to delete cache",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:11.428519+00:00",
  "text": "KeepAlive provide function to delete cache\n\n### What problem does this feature solve?\n\nWe can open multiple tabs. The components corresponding to the tabs use the keepalive cache. We need to destroy the keepalive cache when closing the tabs to release the cache. We also know KeepAlive max property but that can't delete specified cache. hope expose keys and cache property in production\n\n### What does the proposed API look like?\n\nhope expose keys and cache property in production or provide function to delete cache by key",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    ":sparkles: feature request",
    "scope: keep-alive"
  ],
